CustomField.description: The API name of a field set used by the Project Methodology object. This field set defines the methodology fields that are editable when creating a project from a template.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: API name of a field set used by the Methodology object. Fields in this field set define the editable fields in the Methodologies section of the Create Project from Template page.
CustomField.label: Project Methodology Editable
